cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with anomaly detection in video sequences, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes the use of generative models and deep learning techniques, which are common in the sub-categories cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also evaluates the models quantitatively and qualitatively, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
